import React from 'react'; import './index.css' import './script.js' import { blackpices } from './pices/blackpices/exportblackpices.js'; import { whitepices } from './pices/whitepices/exportwhitepices.js'; const App = () => { const [bishopwhite,kingwhite,queenwhite,rookwhite,pawnwhite,knightwhite] = whitepices const [bishop,king,queen,rook,knight,pawn] = blackpices const boardlook = [ ['r', 'n', 'b', 'q', 'k', 'b', 'n', 'r'], ['p', 'p', 'p', 'p', 'p', 'p', 'p', 'p'], [' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '], [' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '], [' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '], [' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '], ['P', 'P', 'P', 'P', 'P', 'P', 'P', 'P'], ['R', 'N', 'B', 'K', 'Q', 'B', 'N', 'R'], ]; let chessSquares = document.querySelectorAll('.chessSquare') // loop over every chess image for drag and drop feature let allPices = document.querySelectorAll('.pices') allPices.forEach(pice => { pice.addEventListener('dragstart', (e) => { pice.classList.add('dragable') }) chessSquares.forEach(square => { square.addEventListener('dragover', (e) => { e.preventDefault() const draggingElement = document.querySelector('.dragable') square.appendChild(draggingElement) }); }) pice.addEventListener('dragend', () => { pice.classList.remove('dragable') }) }) return (
); }; export default App;
